Privacy Policy - MazzyBall
--------------------------


Last updated: January 29, 2026


Developer: JDLK GAMES


This mobile application "MAZZYBALL" is provided by JDLK GAMES and is free with integrated advertisements served via Google AdMob.


We respect your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and with whom we share it.


1. Data Collected

We do **not collect any directly identifiable personal data** (such as name, email, phone number).


However, through Google AdMob (our advertising partner):

- The Android Advertising ID is collected to serve personalized advertisements.

- Anonymous device information (device type, Android version, language, etc.).

- App usage data (views, interactions) to improve ads and measure performance.

- Cookies or similar technologies (web beacons) may be used by Google to deliver advertisements.


This data helps display relevant ads and prevent advertising fraud. No data is used to personally identify you.


2. Data Sharing

- Data collected by AdMob is shared with Google LLC and its advertising partners.

- We do not sell your data to third parties.

- Google may share anonymized data with other advertisers or partners for ad targeting.


3. Personalized Ads and Opt-Out Options

AdMob uses interest-based advertising. You can disable personalized ads:

- On Android: Go to Settings > Google > Ads > Opt out of Ads Personalization.

- Or via Google Ads settings: https://adssettings.google.com


If you opt out, you will still see ads, but they will be less targeted.


4. Other Information

- No other third-party SDKs (analytics, tracking) are used except AdMob.

- No precise location data is collected (except if enabled by AdMob for geo-targeted ads – anonymized).

- Data is stored in the United States and other countries where Google operates, protected under applicable laws.

- We do not use this data for anything other than ads and app functionality.


5. Contact

For any questions about this policy or your data: jluc2805@gmail.com


6. Updates

This policy may be updated. Changes will be posted here and dated.


By using the application, you accept this privacy policy.




